    *** MySQL Assignments ***
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ### TABLES ### (books , authors)

Q. Create a table books and authors.

mysql> select * from books;

+----+------------------+------------+-----------+-----------+---------------+
| id | title            | type       | author_id | editor_id | translator_id |
+----+------------------+------------+-----------+-----------+---------------+
|  1 | Time to Grow Up! | original   |        11 |        21 |          NULL |
|  2 | Your Trip        | translated |        15 |        22 |            32 |
|  3 | Lovely Love      | original   |        14 |        24 |          NULL |
|  4 | Dream Your Life  | original   |        11 |        24 |          NULL |
|  5 | Oranges          | translated |        12 |        25 |            31 |
|  6 | Your Happy Life  | translated |        15 |        22 |            33 |
|  7 | Applied AI       | translated |        13 |        23 |            34 |
|  8 | My Last Book     | original   |        11 |        28 |          NULL |
+----+------------------+------------+-----------+-----------+---------------+


mysql> select * from authors;

+----+------------+-----------+
| id | first_name | last_name |
+----+------------+-----------+
| 11 | Ellen      | Writer    |
| 12 | Olga       | Savelieva |
| 13 | Jack       | Smart     |
| 14 | Donald     | Brain     |
| 15 | Yao        | Dou       |
+----+------------+-----------+


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#    ## INNER JOIN ###

Q . Get batching records from both the tables.

mysql> select books.id,books.title,
        authors.first_name from books 
        inner join authors on books.author_id=
        authors.id;

+----+------------------+------------+
| id | title            | first_name |
+----+------------------+------------+
|  1 | Time to Grow Up! | Ellen      |
|  2 | Your Trip        | Yao        |
|  3 | Lovely Love      | Donald     |
|  4 | Dream Your Life  | Ellen      |
|  5 | Oranges          | Olga       |
|  6 | Your Happy Life  | Yao        |
|  7 | Applied AI       | Jack       |
|  8 | My Last Book     | Ellen      |
+----+------------------+------------+


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ### RIGHT JOIN ###

Q . Get all the records from authors table and only matching records from books table.

mysql> select books.title, books.author_id 
        from books RIGHT JOIN authors ON   
        books.author_id=authors.id;

+------------------+-----------+
| title            | author_id |
+------------------+-----------+
| My Last Book     |        11 |
| Dream Your Life  |        11 |
| Time to Grow Up! |        11 |
| Oranges          |        12 |
| Applied AI       |        13 |
| Lovely Love      |        14 |
| Your Happy Life  |        15 |
| Your Trip        |        15 |
| NULL             |      NULL |
+------------------+-----------+


------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    ### LEFT JOIN ###

Q. Get all the records from books table and only matching records from authors table.

mysql> select books.title, books.author_id 
    from books LEFT JOIN authors ON 
    books.author_id=authors.id;

+------------------+-----------+
| title            | author_id |
+------------------+-----------+
| Time to Grow Up! |        11 |
| Your Trip        |        15 |
| Lovely Love      |        14 |
| Dream Your Life  |        11 |
| Oranges          |        12 |
| Your Happy Life  |        15 |
| Applied AI       |        13 |
| My Last Book     |        11 |
+------------------+-----------+

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
